IN THE HIGH COURT OF PUNJAB & HARYANA, CHANDIGARH

C.W.P. No. 3880 of 1983 Date of Decision: August 2,2007 R.S.Kadian

........Petitioner Versus Union of India and others

..........Respondents Coram:

Hon'ble Mr.Justice Rajesh Bindal Present: Mr.Gaurav Singh,Advocate for the petitioner. Mr.Navneet Singh, AAG, Haryana __ Learned counsel for the petitioner states that the writ petition may be dismissed as having rendered infructuous. Ordered accordingly. (Rajesh Bindal) Judge August 29,2007 arya
